===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|strewen}}, {{m|enm|strawen}}, {{m|enm|streowen}}, from {{inh|en|ang|strewian}}, {{m|ang|strēawian}}, {{m|ang|strēowian||to strew, scatter}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*strawjaną||to strew}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*strew-||to spread, scatter}}. Cognate with {{cog|sco|strow}}, {{m|sco|straw||to strew}}, {{cog|fy|streauwe||to strew}}, {{cog|nl|strooien||to strew, scatter, sprinkle}}, {{cog|de|streuen||to strew, scatter}}, {{cog|sv|strö||to strew}}, {{cog|is|strá||to strew}}, {{cog|nn|strå||to strew}}.

